      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like it\u2019s been kept in a time capsule! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection inside and out. You really have to see it in person to believe how pristine it is. I'm sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come take a look before someone else snaps it up!",
