    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this chassis has been meticulously preserved; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these coupes are known for. Every seal is tight, and the engine bay remains in a concours-ready state, free of heat-cycling wear or fluid seepage.",
